      "span_text": "Using the SAW wavelength of λ SAW = 40 µm, we finally find U zpf = 0.5 × 10 −2 fm, while a theoretical estimation derived from a value reported in [CITATION_1] , along with the effective mode area of the SAW resonator of π × 100 µm × 110 µm, yields U zpf = 1 × 10 −2 fm."
